data.description: What a great deal!!!    Featuring 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, 2 dining areas and nice sized living area with wood burning fireplace.  Great sized lot with mature trees, privacy fence, gazebo and sprinkler system!  Nice open kitchen with stainless appliances including gas range and breakfast nook.   Additional features include gas water heater, gas heating, separate utility room and a great bonus to include solar panels that will be paid off at closing by seller (a $49K savings!).   Come take a look at all this home has to offer, you will be so glad you did!!
